gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 119, Warriors 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Warriors, 119-116.  Devin Booker led the way with 32 points and seven assists for the Suns, while Jusuf Nurkic added 17 points, 13 rebounds and seven assists in the victory.  Stephen Curry tallied 24 points, five rebounds, four assists and four 3PM for the Warriors in the losing effort.  The Suns improve to 13-10 on the season, while the Warriors fall to 10-13
